logic

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.Actor
      • logic.Movable
        • logic.Entity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Collidable, Updatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Enemy, Player

    public abstract class Entity
extends Movable
    An entity has health management and damage. Also it is able to heal and take damage. Entities may have ay invincible period after damage taking.
